io.neba.core.resourcemodels.registration

Class LookupResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.neba.core.resourcemodels.registration.LookupResult

  • public class LookupResult
extends Object
    Represents the result of a lookup of a ResourceModel for a Resource. Provides the found model as an OsgiBeanSource and the resource type the model was found for. The resource type may be any type within the resource's resource type or node type hierarchy.
    Author:
    Olaf Otto
